on-stock-soar\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4702299-why-did-archer-aviation-stock-soar\" target=\"_blank\">with a buy rating</a></span> after it cleared several milestones. Since then, the stock is up more than 85% and is up 128% since <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4697866-archer-aviation-stock-soars-balancing-risks-and-commercial-success\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4697866-archer-aviation-stock-soars-balancing-risks-and-commercial-success\" target=\"_blank\">my buy rating from a month earlier</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155397246/image_2155397246.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743405-archer-aviation-bullish-future-despite-stellantis-turmoil", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 23:43:28"}, {"id": "4743402", "title": "Tarsus Pharmaceuticals: Early Rollout Exceeding Expectations", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Life Science Investing\" data-id=\"155151969\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"715px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Bill Oxford</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>When I last looked at <b>Tarsus Pharmaceuticals, Inc. (</b><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TARS\" title=\"Tarsus Pharmaceuticals, Inc.\">TARS</a></span><b>)</b> in April of this year, I concluded that <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4695999-following-up-on-tarsus-pharmaceuticals\"><strong>article</strong></a> by saying I was maintaining a small \u201cwatch item\u201d holding in the name. I added I would circle back</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743402-tarsus-pharmaceuticals-early-rollout-exceeding-expectations", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 23:31:22"}, {"id": "4743398", "title": "Candy Crush: Hershey's M&A Buzz Is Just The Cherry On Top", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A candy store museum in Hershey, Pennsylvania\" data-id=\"1164904198\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Cheri Alguire</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>I like <strong>The Hershey Company (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HSY\" title=\"The Hershey Company\">HSY</a></span>)</strong>, as the title of my most recent <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4697143-going-coco-for-hersheys-a-path-to-double-digit-returns-for-this-dividend-gem\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4697143-going-coco-for-hersheys-a-path-to-double-digit-returns-for-this-dividend-gem\" target=\"_blank\">article</a> on June 3 had the bullish title, <em>\"Going Coco For Hershey's: A Path To Double-Digit Returns For This Dividend Gem.\" </em></p> <p>As it turns out, I'm not</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743398-candy-crush-hersheys-m-and-a-buzz-is-just-the-cherry-on-top", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 23:19:12"}, {"id": "4743395", "title": "THW: Revisiting The 11.8% Healthcare Yielder As Thesis Plays Out", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Medical Exam\" data-id=\"1345550980\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">You Have A Case Of Yielditis. Keep Hand Away From Fist.</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">filadendron/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>We first wrote about abrdn World Healthcare Fund (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/THW\" title=\"abrdn World Healthcare Fund\">THW</a></span>) 18 months back. We saw an unwarranted optimism on the fund coupled with faulty logic that made it a target for showing \"the other side\". While we have used some creative titles, this one</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743395-thw-revisiting-the-11-percent-healthcare-yielder-as-thesis-plays-out", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 23:14:36"}, {"id": "4743391", "title": "Alaska Airlines Stock Surges 15% On Bullish Outlook", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Alaska Airlines Boeing 737.\" data-id=\"1523412783\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1136px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">DaveAlan</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Alaska Airli<span class=\"highlighted_text\">nes (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ALK\" title=\"Alaska Air Group, Inc.\">ALK</a></span>) h</span>as released its strategy update ahead of its Investor Day and investors seem to like what the company presented as the stock is trading 14% higher at the time of writing. In this report, I will be reviewing</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743391-alaska-airlines-stock-surges-15-percent-on-bullish-outlook", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 23:03:13"}, {"id": "4743390", "title": "L3Harris Is Likely To Benefit From Increased Defense Spending Amid U.S.-China Tensions", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Leadership\" data-id=\"501650629\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"853px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">olm26250/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In my recent <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4737287-northrop-grumman-priming-for-offense-when-its-not-needed\">Northrop Grumman Corporation</a> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NOC\" title=\"Northrop Grumman Corporation\">NOC</a>) analysis I outlined a case for lower defense spending amid geopolitical peace through diplomacy, particularly in Ukraine. However, my ongoing research and feedback from mentors have refined my worldview. L3Harris</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743390-l3harris-benefit-from-increased-defense-spending-amid-tensions", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 22:57:22"}, {"id": "4743389", "title": "Henry Schein: The Kind Of Business I Like But No Margin Of Safety Now", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dentist, woman and patient with tools for teeth whitening, oral hygiene and consultation with mask. Healthcare, specialist and person for mouth wellness, dental service and check for gum bacteria\" data-id=\"1939508769\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"810px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Kobus Louw/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>For me, the U.S. stock market is undoubtedly the place to invest. However, it is also arguably overpriced at the moment. Based on Morningstar's analysts' assessment as of December 6, 2024, the U.S. market is 6.9% overvalued.</p> <p>The Shiller</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743389-henry-schein-the-kind-of-business-i-like-but-no-margin-of-safety-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 22:52:58"}, {"id": "4743387", "title": "Westrock Coffee: Not Enough Progress And Uncertainty Ahead", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397854643/image_1397854643.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Coffee beans\" data-id=\"1397854643\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1151px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397854643/image_1397854643.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397854643/image_1397854643.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s